Interface ElementGenerator<OBJ>

  • Type Parameters:
    OBJ - the type of domain object
    All Known Implementing Classes:

    public interface ElementGenerator<OBJ>
    An ElementGenerator converts domain objects to Elements and vice versa.

    Implementations should be JSON serialisable.
